<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Mount Pleasant</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">The beautifully treed community offers a wide range of housing options including wartime bungalows, townhomes, apartment condos and new in-fill homes as well. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Homes for sale in Mount Pleasant are typically listed at an affordable price of around $700,000 with the high-end properties available for as much as $1.5 million. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">The lovely 160 hectares crescent-shaped Confederation Park to the north of the community offers abundant recreational opportunities for the residents.</p>


